{"tid":1767623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急] 你班連登仔同我入黎睇哂佢","createTime":"2019-12-03T12:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T16:03:19.000Z","uid":63382,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"348803cb0755d9e594f08c7893fb4040f74f335f","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:27:22.000Z","msg":"眼見半年間五毛網軍人數大增，分化手段層出不窮<br />\n我係到綜合左呢半年五毛常用分化手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）基本上都係不斷放負同失敗主義，通常都係一班湧出黎起風，呢班好低裝，容易睇得出<br />\n<br />\n2）扮演最激進同最溫和示威者，當有不利消息就放稻草人出黎鳩屌割蓆，休息撚已經係最好例子<br />\n<br />\n3）不斷貼fake news同農場文，斷章取義做標題撚引戰鳩屌，仲會有大量甜post，務求霸佔熱門<br />\n<br />\n4）散播未真係FC既資訊／活動煽動人，挑起你地仇恨同不斷訴諸暴力／裝修<br />\n<br />\n5）呢種高級五毛係會打一大篇文作故仔，例如扮被捕者同勇武，文中滲透白色恐怖同失敗主義，之前中環被捕果post之後被手足踢爆係最好例子<br />\n<br />\n好多五毛依家都好醒，平時開下新聞同即場討論post講下人話笑下黑警<br />\n到關鍵時候就起風分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢地好有系統，有一班ac負責開post就長期開post<br />\n但回post推post果班通常呢半年以黎無開過post／彊屍ac，幫手推上熱門<br />\n每晚深夜呢個現象好常見，因為人小好容易制造輿論起風，等你地起身硬食風向<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">講咁多我唔係要大家捉五毛<br />\n我只想大家上連登唔該保持獨立思考同分析<br />\n唔好盲目相信所有post</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門比多啲人知"},{"pid":"c8427917fd827fae3f06c28fd17517bfdb39e331","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e47b2cba096ce055ab2a3933d1530202bf0efb1","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8364d04c9aa939b764eeb81d7f2a13bf2e0191","tid":1767623,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a4039a932ea970933dd1d963246d4a9b09725ed","tid":1767623,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:31:32.000Z","msg":"岩先民記po都推唔郁 冇咩人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ef61bed7309e2aff702dc318af35f9c5ad1b7","tid":1767623,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"［twitter戰線］美國嘈緊中共網絡監控同滲透<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=6224fe87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></span> 攞Tweets"},{"pid":"2de43bfd67a8c92e3da65ba3a704fde56767bfe9","tid":1767623,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"第28次民間記招慘變condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd3e5cb8f82cb5660ce96c9d27d6057e7490f3f","tid":1767623,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"不論咩毛<br />\n我只會狙擊畜生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好太旨意網主<br />\n檢舉+瘋狂引用(draw attention)都夠<br />\n好讓大家思考"},{"pid":"36871bafebd85ca6ac9fc8772faa5424fdb38033","tid":1767623,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38d0c63e72bc349d6f0189a8d902012a77927781","tid":1767623,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6b7f02a82365e3da99686dc641e291a53c708b99","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e409e81394834c7e181780f9e951572128ba2dc9","tid":1767623,"uid":59609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0677559f7d7e537ae0161203ac1920f7f8e76fcc","tid":1767623,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7646bc1a843e61e894f0aff14686e07ec5e5a9c","tid":1767623,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b3679dd88e388c8bc626177d43ac756f537b6fd","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f79aca36531686c4f48ad7328a7d271b9b0c38","tid":1767623,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［請廣傳］<br />\n和理非目前可以做到嘅事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先推12月8號嘅民陣遊行：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vYYe0AE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvYYe0AE.jpg&h=893a72a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一.）義士唔係condom！強烈建議香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">即時停止再月捐所有喺今次革命奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織</span>，將啲錢用喺更加有用嘅地方上面，例如揸車接放學嘅油費、飯券、法庭訟費、醫療開支、FA嘅物資費用等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織例子：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">宣明會</span><br />\n（2018善款超過9.1億）：有巴絲post CUT捐回覆，「oh好遺憾」<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">無國界醫生</span><br />\n（2017總收入超5億）：有巴絲post非新聞稿答覆，達哥式回應（一直有mon住關注情況，屌你你mon到香港淪陷埋先出手不如）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（無恥界醫生條熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut）</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">樂施會</span><br />\n（2017總收入超2.5億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: gold;\">奧比斯香港</span><br />\n（2018年總收入超2.1億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: gold;\">UNICEF HK</span><br />\n（2017年總收入超1.7億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: gold;\">Save the Children</span><br />\n （2017年總收入超1.6億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n7. <span style=\"color: gold;\">香港紅十字會</span><br />\n（2017/18年總收入超1.4億）：18/8出咗份聲明，借世界人道主義日輕輕帶過呼籲各方克制，過去兩個多月動員逾800人次做電話熱線加現場支援<a href=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress_room%2Fpress_release_2019%2F201908182.html&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=8bfe01e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html</a><br />\n8. <span style=\"color: gold;\">國際培幼會</span><br />\n（2017年總收入近8000萬）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二.）本地文宣上，各區連儂牆近日被大肆清拆，各位香港人可以喺朝早人多時份重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三.）請大家持續喺國際文宣上着力（Twitter, FB, IG），呼籲國際社會支持香港示威者五大訴求，順便將黑警惡行/ 中共建政70年嚟種種歷史惡行公諸於世"},{"pid":"9dc8141c22669413c65d16cdf5e70d738eb0c4be","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc785ce91dfe7d228e4b1254f11d49ab67b85f85","tid":1767623,"uid":54965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eacb3e6efab4b4a86934830f4eaefe33d0598c3","tid":1767623,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d0dfeaf712840eccefb04f4bfea5543cf76e1","tid":1767623,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}